149
00:11:23,866 --> 00:11:26,866
Here comes a young man who can help.

150
00:11:26,866 --> 00:11:28,066
- This is tiring.
- Come on now.

151
00:11:28,066 --> 00:11:30,266
- Grab me properly. Use your strength.
- Stand up straight.

152
00:11:30,900 --> 00:11:35,300
Villagers came together
to get ready for the new year.

153
00:11:35,300 --> 00:11:38,166
As the produce was neatly stacked,

154
00:11:38,166 --> 00:11:40,233
