- Okay.

156
00:11:49,866 --> 00:11:51,566
Dr. Gu, it's ready.

157
00:11:51,833 --> 00:11:54,566
- You can inject the anesthetics.
- Okay.

158
00:11:58,733 --> 00:12:00,233
Everyone was in their setting...

159
