(Village shelter)

168
00:13:30,866 --> 00:13:32,100
Walk slowly.

169
00:13:33,433 --> 00:13:35,966
Seon In Ho, Yang Chang Ju.

170
00:13:35,966 --> 00:13:36,900
Get in first.

171
00:13:36,900 --> 00:13:38,133
- Choi Dae Woong.
- What's going on?

172
00:13:38,133 --> 00:13:40,466
Get in first and we'll let you know.

173
00:13:58,933 --> 00:14:02,566
We're currently figuring out
the situation.

174
00:14:02,566 --> 00:14:05,933
Let's wait until our safety is secured.

175
00:14:05,933 --> 00:14:09,033
Jun Mo, I don't see Mr. Piano
and Comrade Na Gyeong.

176
00:14:09,766 --> 00:14:10,700
