184
00:15:40,233 --> 00:15:42,400
Should we head back?

185
00:15:44,800 --> 00:15:47,733
We better go back.

186
00:15:49,600 --> 00:15:51,433
Okay, let's go.

187
00:16:09,700 --> 00:16:11,600
They went together in a car.

188
00:16:11,600 --> 00:16:13,100
I'm sure they're safe somewhere.

189
00:16:14,266 --> 00:16:15,766
They should be fine.

190
00:16:20,933 --> 00:16:23,033
