193
00:16:39,533 --> 00:16:40,733
The sound stopped.

194
00:16:42,500 --> 00:16:44,866
You two go and have a look.

195
00:16:45,800 --> 00:16:46,866
Be careful.

196
00:16:47,300 --> 00:16:48,400
- Okay.
- Okay.

