I'll try again.

260
00:20:53,233 --> 00:20:55,500
Teach me.

261
00:20:55,500 --> 00:20:57,266
I'll try again.

262
00:20:57,266 --> 00:20:58,366
Okay.

263
00:21:00,200 --> 00:21:01,700
It can be hard.

264
00:21:04,833 --> 00:21:06,166
The rice cake is here.

265
00:21:29,933 --> 00:21:31,866
I'm glad to see this day.

266
00:21:31,866 --> 00:21:35,933
We all gathered to spend
Christmas together.

267
00:21:35,933 --> 00:21:38,033
Jun Mo, it's so touching.

